<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Sarge</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/logo.png">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('navbar', {currentPage: 'About'}); %>

    <h1 class="ta-c">About Sarge</h1>
    <h2 class="ta-c">Michael C. Kavcak</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
        <div>
            <h3>Senior Computer Engineer | ASIC Specialist</h3>
            <p>With over three decades in the computer and semiconductor industries, Michael C. Kavcak, affectionately known as "Sarge" by colleagues for his decisive leadership, exemplifies dedication and expertise. His assertive approach ensures disciplined execution and impeccable outcomes across all projects.</p>
            <h4>Professional Highlights</h4>
            <ul>
                <li><span class="bold">Expertise:</span> Sarge's extensive educational background and varied work experiences provide him with a robust knowledge base, enabling him to quickly adapt to new challenges, regardless of complexity.</li>
                <li><span class="bold">Continuous Learning:</span> He keeps abreast of the latest advancements in application-specific integrated circuits (ASICs) and hardware verification languages (HVLs) through ongoing professional development, including seminars and industry conferences.</li>
                <li><span class="bold">Community Involvement:</span> Active participation in Austin's DVclub underscores his commitment to staying at the forefront of verification trends.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <img src="/images/Sarge.jpeg" alt="Sarge" class="img-sarge">
    </div>
    <div class="grid-2">
        <img src="/images/sarge_awards.jpg" alt="Awards" class="img-sarge">
        <div>
            <h3>Education</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>B.S. in Computer Engineering, Penn State University, Graduated with Distinction, 1990</li>
                <li>M.S. in Electrical Engineering, University of Texas at Austin, 1992</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Career Path</h3>
            <p><span class="bold">Established Industry Presence:</span> Sarge has held significant roles in major firms like AMD, Apple, and SMSC.</p>
            <p><span class="bold">Consulting Expertise:</span> As a consultant, his strategic insights have benefitted high-profile clients such as Toshiba, Boeing, and Cadence.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="cta-box">
            <h3>Hobbies</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Men's Austin Baseball League</li>
                <li>Handy Wheels volunteer</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Explore More</h3>
            <a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a>
            <a href="/services">Services</a>
        </div>
        <img src="/images/baseball.jpeg" alt="Baseball" class="img-sarge">
    </div>
    
    <%- include('footer', {currentPage: 'About'}); %>
</body>
</html>
<style>
    body{
        width: 100%;
    }
    .grid-2{
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 20px;
        margin: 20px;
    }
    .img-sarge{
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 10px;
        align-self: center;
    }
    .bold{
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    p, li{
        line-height: 1.5;
    }
    li:not(:last-child) {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .cta-box{
        background-color:var(--primary);
        padding: 24px;
        margin: 72px auto;
        width: fit-content;
        border-radius: 8px;
        border: 2px solid var(--text);
    }
    .cta-box a{
        color: var(--background);
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0 16px;
        padding: 8px 16px;
        background-color: var(--secondary);
        border-radius: 4px;
        font-size: var(--h4-font-size);
    }
    .cta-box a:hover{
        background-color: var(--secondary-hover);
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    @media (max-width: 875px){
        .grid-2{
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>